Majin Buu is a fictional character and final antagonist in the Dragon Ball manga and anime series. He was created by Akira Toriyama to be the most powerful villain encountered by the heroes. Majin Buu has various forms including Kid Buu, Super Buu, and Good Buu, and has near-invincible regenerative abilities. He was originally awakened by the wizard Bibidi and aims to destroy everything in his path.
